Red         -255...255                      shift-value for the red component
Green       -255...255                      shift-value for the green component
Blue        -255...255                      shift-value for the green component
Contrast    -255...255                      contrast-value, negative values decrease the contrast
Bright      -255...255                      shift value for all color-channels
